- if @users.present?
  %p
    Do you want to unfollow all the users below?

    = form_tag(home_unfollow_users_path, method: 'post') do
      = hidden_field_tag 'users_ids', @users.map { |user| user['id'] }.join(',')
      = button_tag 'Unfollow users'

Users who aren't following you back:

- if @users.present?
  - @users.each do |user|
    %p
      %span= link_to user['screen_name'], "http://twitter.com/#{user['screen_name']}"

- else
  %p
    None
